%F A242986 Asymptotic: a(x) ~ exp(x*log(2) - log(Pi)/2 - cos(Pi*x)*(log(x/2) + 1/(2*x))/2 + log(6*(x+1)) - log(3+floor(x/2))) for x>=1.
